query:
SELECT j.id, j.customerEmail, j.status, j.serviceType, j.createdAt, u.id as userId, u.email as userEmail
FROM jobs j
LEFT JOIN users u ON j.customerId = u.id
WHERE j.customerEmail = '12@customer.com' OR u.email = '12@customer.com'
ORDER BY j.createdAt DESC
LIMIT 5;
